---
title: Masa Corn Pancakes
servings: 2
tags:
  - breakfast
source:
  name: YouTube
  url: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YCDVNx2bfOk
---

Crack @eggs{2} in a #bowl{}, add @water{1%cup}, @salt{0.5%tsp}, and @sugar{2%tbsp}.

Whisk/beat the mixture well.

Add @masa flour{0.5%cup} and mix well.

Let sit for ~{30%minutes}.

Make pancakes in a #pan{} with @oil{2%tbsp}.
